Name: ACE32
Description: The ACE32 is a versatile assault rifle known for its reliability and power. It is widely used in military operations. The weapon offers a balanced combination of damage and ease of handling, making it suitable for both close and long-range combat.

Name: AK47
Description: The AK47 is one of the most iconic rifles worldwide. Known for its durability and power, it is favored by military forces and shooters alike. Its high damage output makes it a top choice for combat scenarios requiring brute force.

Name: AUG
Description: The AUG is a high-tech assault rifle designed for precision and accuracy. With its integrated optics and powerful rounds, this weapon excels in long-range engagements while maintaining versatility in close combat.

Name: AWM

Name: Berreta686

Name: BizonPP19

Name: Crossbow

Name: DP12
Description: The DP-12 is a double-barrel pump-action shotgun, providing exceptional firepower in close-quarter combat. Its dual-barrel design allows for rapid firing, making it a formidable weapon for self-defense and tactical use.

Name: DP28
Description: The DP-28 is a reliable light machine gun, historically used in many military conflicts. Its durable design and large ammunition capacity make it a valuable asset in sustained firefights.

Name: Dragunov
Description: The Dragunov is a semi-automatic sniper rifle renowned for its accuracy and durability. It is widely used by military forces for long-range precision, offering a perfect balance of power and reliability.
